msgid "# `pgroonga.enable_crash_safe` parameter"
msgstr "# `pgroonga.enable_crash_safe`パラメーター"

msgid "Since 2.3.3."
msgstr "2.3.3で追加。"

msgid "## Summary"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"`pgroonga.enable_crash_safe` parameter controls whether crash safe feature is "
"enabled or not."
msgstr "`pgroonga.enable_crash_safe`パラメーターはクラッシュセーフ機能を有効にするかどうかを制御します。"

msgid ""
"Note that you must add [`pgroonga_crash_safer` module][pgroonga-crash-safer] t"
"o [`shared_preload_libraries` parameter][postgresql-shared-preload-libraries] "
"value when you set `on` to `pgroonga.enable_crash_safe` parameter."
msgstr ""
"`pgroonga.enable_crash_safe`パラメーターに`on`を設定したときは[`shared_preload_libraries`パラメー"
"ター][postgresql-shared-preload-libraries]に[`pgroonga_crash_safer`モジュール][pgroong"
"a-crash-safer]を指定しなければいけません。"

msgid "See also: [Crash safe][crash-safe]"
msgstr "参考：[クラッシュセーフ][crash-safe]"

msgid "## Syntax"
msgstr "## 構文"

msgid "You must set `pgroonga.enable_crash_safe` in `postgresql.conf`:"
msgstr "`postgresql.conf`で`pgroonga.enable_crash_safe`を設定しなければいけません。"

msgid ""
"```text\n"
"pgroonga.enable_crash_safe = boolean\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"`boolean` is a boolean value. There are some literals for boolean value such a"
"s `on`, `off`, `true`, `false`, `yes` and `no`."
msgstr "`boolean`は真偽値です。真偽値には`on`、`off`、`true`、`false`、`yes`、`no`のようなリテラルがあります。"

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使い方"

msgid "Here is an example configration to enable crash safe feature:"
msgstr "以下はクラッシュセーフ機能を有効にする設定の例です。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"shared_preload_libraries = 'pgroonga_crash_safer'\n"
"pgroonga.enable_crash_safe = on\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

